{"tid":1152827,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[化學物] 喜茶廈門分店被揭衞生惡劣 只要好飲就得","createTime":"2019-05-13T08:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T09:39:26.000Z","uid":51620,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"647ef0478ed3812eebd50af39337ffecf03b23b8","tid":1152827,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T08:42:59.000Z","msg":"中國連鎖飲品店「喜茶HEYTEA」的福建廈門華潤萬象城分店，日前被衞生部門抽查時，揭發多項衞生指標不合格，引起輿論熱議。<span style=\"color: red;\">惟中國記者上周六（11日）到涉事門店走訪時，發現店外仍大排長龍，更有顧客表示︰「只要好喝就行。」</span><br />\n<br />\n根據當局通報，執法人員抽查該分店後廚時，發現後廚地面積水多，且水果等食材未有按規定離地10厘米擺放；更嚴重的是，執法人員抽驗一次性飲品杯，及擺放水果的容器時，<span style=\"color: red;\">更發現容器ATP指數（ATP是三磷酸腺苷的縮寫）嚴重超標。</span><br />\n<br />\n執法人員其後責令該分店立即整改，同時督促其改進消毒方法，注意餐飲具及盛放食材容器的清洗消毒。<br />\n<br />\n事件曝光後，引起不少網民嘩然。惟內地記者發現該分店外的人潮依舊，外賣員亦指訂單仍然很多。有顧客受訪時坦言，早已得知該分店衞生不達標，但仍不擔心，「就是喝不到這個（飲料）不罷休」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />落左D咩野拎到非飲不可?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190513/bkn-20190513011007952-0513_00952_001.html?fbclid=IwAR3ThWXs0cx-h4s4bo-jUggg2ymtbkCMdAC4-hGB0IHR0Ehjn66z0o__AXY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190513%2Fbkn-20190513011007952-0513_00952_001.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3ThWXs0cx-h4s4bo-jUggg2ymtbkCMdAC4-hGB0IHR0Ehjn66z0o__AXY&d=JinSrGH%2FoctmVpTuEhnihNxiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=9ff91569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190513/bkn-20190513011007952-0513_00952_001.html?fbclid=IwAR3ThWXs0cx-h4s4bo-jUggg2ymtbkCMdAC4-hGB0IHR0Ehjn66z0o__AXY</a>"},{"pid":"93e27933288d712f0ccd56ee4c11e798b5f93587","tid":1152827,"uid":11798,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T08:44:36.000Z","msg":"大麻，我加了大麻.jpg"},{"pid":"eb0a62841d48aa78a4136208f6d1c6f3fc75c5bf","tid":1152827,"uid":130695,"like":0,"disli